#

Butter Chicken with Basmati Rice and Garlic Naan

$18.99
800 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

DairyGlutenNuts

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinComfort Food

Tags:

Indian CuisineComfort FoodRich Flavors

Description

A rich and creamy butter chicken served with fragrant basmati rice and soft garlic naan for a delightful culinary experience.

Ingredients

  • Chicken thighs: 1.5 lbs
  • Butter: 1/2 cup
  • Heavy cream: 1 cup
  • Tomato puree: 1 cup
  • Garlic cloves: 4, minced
  • Ginger: 1 inch, grated
  • Onion: 1, finely chopped
  • Basmati rice: 2 cups
  • Garlic naan: 4 pieces
  • Garam masala: 1 tbsp
  • Cumin: 1 tsp
  • Coriander: 1 tsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Cilantro: for garnish
